{"title":"冬天的日子","authors":["熊明修熊福林"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊明修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿得像春的心事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫我怀想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫身居闹市的人们怀想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在朴素的诗行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施下一些养分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后去领略"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于我的那一份清香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种你的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有一双妙手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你从荒原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引向广袤大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从发芽返青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引向吐穗的花期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引发出许许多多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相依为命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深入浅出的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随你两片细嫩的叶子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感激的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陷入遐思——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种永世不绝的血源　来自冬日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片鲜绿无比的麦浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回乡村一趟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着冬天的道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从不夜的都市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到庄稼最原始的根部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时分娩过秋天的田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同往年一样沉静而清凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而小麦与新活的油菜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却给了我希望和色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟在拐弯的地方袅着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人依然在无风的檐下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煨着阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲自鸡鸣犬吠中走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍老掩饰不住惊喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一杯茶里坐下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲告诉我今年的谷子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然可以饱一年的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芝麻和大豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也喂实了去年的泥缸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是钱袋被化肥和农药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啃得有点消瘦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回乡村一趟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾满声光与电子的思想和情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才又一次被泥土拭亮"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}